\par }\pard\plain \s15\qj\nowidctlpar\adjustright \lang2057 {<#/>This accusation is sometimes used on platforms by politicians just to show people that they are advocates of <-_citizens><+_citizens\rquote > rights.
\par }\pard\plain \qj\nowidctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang1031 {<#/>}{\fs24\lang2057 But in fact they are not. <#/>There are so many instances where people have been detained by politicians without being prosecuted.
