\par }{\fs24\lang2057 <#/>About 4.4 billion condoms will be used annually in the world mostly in the developing countries during the 1990,s }{\b\v\fs24\lang2057 <&/>punct}{\fs24\lang2057  as a protective measure against AIDS and othe
